output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to the given criteria:
1. Has CMF: Yes, it has CMF 11240017 at the end of the post.
2. Refers to candidate: Yes, specifically mentions Marcel Ciolacu multiple times, who is a presidential candidate.
3. Addresses wide population: Yes, this is a paid advertisement with a large reach (200,000-250,000 impressions) targeting the Iași population.
4. Electoral objective: Yes, the post promotes PSD and Marcel Ciolacu's achievements, positioning them as the "only sure way for Iași" and criticizing the liberal administration.
5. Journalism: No, this is clearly promotional content rather than journalistic material.
6. Personal opinion: No, this is an official party communication with a CMF number, paid for by PSD Iași.
This post constitutes electoral propaganda because: - It's a paid political advertisement - Has a CMF number - Directly promotes a presidential candidate (Marcel Ciolacu) - Makes electoral promises and claims - Criticizes political opponents - Is clearly meant to influence voter opinion
Since the presidential campaign period has ended and this post is still running after November 23, 2024, 18:00, it violates Article 55 t).

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This is clearly electoral propaganda as it: 1. Contains official party messaging (CMF number) 2. Promotes a presidential candidate 3. Makes electoral promises 4. Criticizes opposition 5. Is a paid advertisement targeting a large audience
conclusion.message-for-police: PSD Iași, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin continuarea propagandei electorale după încheierea campaniei electorale pentru alegerile prezidențiale, prin promovarea unui material publicitar plătit (ID Facebook: 586428570613663) care îl prezintă în mod favorabil pe candidatul prezidențial Marcel Ciolacu, după ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024. Materialul conține număr CMF (11240017), face promisiuni electorale și critică oponenții politici, având un evident caracter de propagandă electorală pentru candidatul prezidențial al PSD.
